This versatile PNY Elite-X 1TB USB 3.1 flash drive is backward-compatible with USB 3.0 and USB 2.0 ports on Mac and PCs for simple transfers.

fields.name: ASUS - ROG MAXIMUS XIII HERO Socket LGA 1200 USB 3.2 Intel Motherboard
fields.description: ROG provides you with the very best gaming-audio inputs and outputs, with special shielded designs, and a collection of carefully selected professional-grade audio components

fields.name: EVGA - X299 Dark (Socket LGA2066) USB 3.1 Intel Motherboard
fields.description: Overclock with confidence by using this EATX-size EVGA motherboard. It supports up to 64GB of RAM for efficient multitasking capability and Intel's X299 chipset for speedy processing power. This EVGA motherboard has eight native USB 3.0 ports for connecting accessories, and its eight SATA ports provide plenty of room for essential hard drives.

fields.name: MSI - AMD Radeon RX 6700 XT GAMING X 12G - 12GB GDDR6 - PCI Express 4.0 - Graphics Card
fields.description: THE GAMING YOU KNOW & TRUST The latest iteration of MSI’s iconic GAMING series once again brings performance, low-noise efficiency, and aesthetics that hardcore gamers have come to recognize and trust. Now you too can enjoy all your favorite games with a powerful graphics card that stays cool and silent. Just the way you like it. It’s time to put on team colors. Synchronize lighting with other compatible devices to take the light show to another level. Going dark is as easy as turning the lights off. WE KEEP IT COOL AND QUIET The TWIN FROZR 8 thermal system has been designed for efficiency. Expect a perfect balance of cool and quiet for more fun during endless gaming sessions. TORX FAN 4.0 is built on teamwork, with pairs of fan blades bound together with an outer ring design link that focuses airflow into the updated TWIN FROZR 8 cooling system. Core Pipes are precision-machined for maximum contact over the GPU and spread the heat along the full length of the heatsink for optimal cooling. Stay stealthy with Airflow Control that improves airflow dynamics. Deflectors provide additional surface area and guide air to where it’s needed for maximum cooling. Wave-curved 2.0 fin edges disrupt unwanted airflow harmonics resulting in reduced noise.

fields.name: GIGABYTE - AMD Radeon RX 6800 XT GAMING OC 16GB GDDR6 PCI Express 4.0 Graphics Card
fields.description: GIGABYTE AMD Radeon RX 6800 XT GAMING OC 16G graphics card delivers ultra-high frame rates and serious 4K gameplay. Get the ultimate gaming experience with powerful new compute units, amazing AMD Infinity Cache, and up to 16GB of dedicated GDDR6 memory. And, when paired with an AMD Ryzen 5000 Series desktop processor, AMD Smart Access Memory technology offers new levels of gaming performance.

fields.name: GIGABYTE - AMD Radeon RX 6900 XT 16G GAMING OC GDDR6 PCI Express 4.0 Graphics Card -Black
fields.description: GIGABYTE AMD Radeon RX 6900 XT GAMING OC 16G graphics card delivers ultra-high frame rates and serious 4K gameplay. Get the ultimate gaming experience with powerful new compute units, amazing AMD Infinity Cache, and up to 16GB of dedicated GDDR6 memory. And, when paired with an AMD Ryzen 5000 Series desktop processor, AMD Smart Access Memory technology offers new levels of gaming performance.

fields.name: CyberPowerPC - Gamer Xtreme Desktop - Intel Core i7-11700F - 16GB Memory - NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 Ti - 1TB HDD + 500GB SSD - Black
fields.description: One-up the competition with this CyberPowerPC Gamer Xtreme gaming desktop. The 500GB SSD and 1TB HDD offer rapid app loading and ample storage space for your collection, while the Intel Core i7 processor and 16GB of RAM support effortless multitasking. This CyberPowerPC Gamer Xtreme gaming desktop features an NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 Ti graphics card for high frame rates when gaming.

fields.name: Lenovo - Legion Tower 5 AMD Gaming Desktop - AMD Ryzen 7-5700G - 16GB Memory - NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 - 512GB SSD + 1TB HDD - Raven Black
fields.description: Engineered out of a passion for savage power and unmatched speed, the Lenovo Legion Tower 5 AMD delivers mind-blowing performance that combines AMD Ryzen processors and top-of-the-line NVIDIA GeForce graphics cards for blazing-fast frame rates at up to 4K resolution. Pushing far beyond the upper bounds of smaller rig configurations while keeping things cool and whisper quiet, the Legion Tower 5 is a marvel of build and design, accentuated by its illuminated blue LED logo and lighting, as well a transparent side panel that can properly showcase your internals.

fields.name: iBUYPOWER - TraceMR Gaming Desktop - Intel i7 11700F - 16GB Memory - NVIDIA RTX 3060Ti 8GB - 480GB SSD + 1TB HDD
fields.description: Upgrade your current gaming rig with this iBUYPOWER Desktop. It’s 16GB of RAM and Intel i7-11700F processor let you run multiple programs at once, and its NVIDIA RTX 3060Ti card renders fast-paced action smoothly without screen tearing. This iBUYPOWER desktop also has a 480GB solid state drive and 1TB hard drive for saving your favorite games.

fields.name: CybertronPC - BLU-Print Desktop - AMD Ryzen ThreadRipper 2990WX - 128GB Memory - 1TB Solid State Drive + 4 x 1TB Solid State Drives - Black/RGB
fields.description: CybertronPC BLU-Print Desktop: Create the ultimate workstation with this Cybertron PC BLU-Print workstation desktop. The dual QUADRO RTX 6000 graphics cards render projects with blazing speed and in extreme detail, while the 1TB NVME M.2 and four 1TB SSDs in RAID 10 configuration offer fast load times. This Cybertron PC BLU-Print workstation desktop has a 32-core AMD Ryzen Threadripper 2990WX processor for heavy multitasking and video production.

fields.name: HP OMEN - 30L Gaming Desktop - AMD Ryzen 5 - 16GB Memory - NVIDIA® GeForce RTX™ 3060 - 1TB SSD - Shadow Black
fields.description: With great power comes this: The OMEN 30L Gaming Desktop PC lives for the thrill of the chase, never leaves a friend behind, and makes a mean midnight snack of action and adventure. Meet your new best friend, packing an AMD Ryzen™ processor and a NVIDIA® GeForce® RTX graphics card. Do how you do: OMEN Gaming Hub’s growing list of customization and optimization features gives you the power to dial-in your game and tailor-make your mark. With OMEN Light Studio, you can tailor make everything with your mark. Your game never looked so good: Sure, it's what's inside that counts, but it's what's outside that gets the looks. With tempered glass front and side panels, a full-metal frame, and complete RGB control, we made this PC for people who know that style points count on the final scoreboard of life.

fields.name: ASUS - ROG 16" WQXGA 165Hz Gaming Laptop - Intel Core i9 - 16GB Memory - NVIDIA RTX3060 - 1TB SSD - Off Black
fields.description: ASUS ROG Gaming Laptop. Enjoy everyday gaming with this ASUS notebook PC. The 11th Gen Intel Core i9 processor and 16GB of RAM let you run graphics-heavy games smoothly, while the potent NVIDIA RTX3060 graphics produce high-quality visuals on the new fast 16-inch 165hz WQXGA display. This ASUS notebook PC has 1TB SSD that shortens load times and offers ample storage.

fields.name: GIGABYTE - 15.6" 4K OLED Creator Laptop - Intel Core i7-11800H - 16GB - NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3060 1TB SSD
fields.description: AERO laptops reach the balance between high performance and portability, which is crucial for creators. They are equipped with the latest CPU that integrates the Thunderbolt 4 interface and supports new PCIe Gen4 SSDs as well as Wi-Fi 6, resulting in significant enhancements in performance and transmission rate. AERO laptops also possess world-leading dual-certified color calibrated displays with X-Rite™ color calibration and Pantone® Validated certification. Render quicker, broadcast clearer, and edit videos better with NVIDIA GPUs in Studio laptops and desktops.

fields.name: MSI - 17.3" Gaming Laptop - Intel Core i9 - 32 GB Memory - NVIDIA RTX A5000 - 1 TB SSD - Titanium Blue
fields.description: MSI mobile workstation offers you a reliable and versatile solution for boosting your workflow from concept to final production. Seamlessly work on large-scale computations and graphics-intensive applications. MSI Mobile workstations are ISV certified systems, which ensures that both hardware and software are fully stable and compatible for a professional experience.

fields.name: NZXT - H710i eATX Mid-Tower Case with Tempered Glass - Red/Matte Black
fields.description: Create a professional-grade PC with this black and red NZXT ATX mid-tower case. The front panel USB-C connector supports the connection of USB 3.1 Gen 2 devices to a front-facing port, while the NZXT CAM application lets you monitor the installation process. This NZXT ATX mid-tower case has a GPU mounting bracket to showcase your graphics card.

fields.name: Thermaltake - Level 20 RS Motherboard Sync ARGB ATX Mid Tower Gaming Computer Case with 2 200mm RGB Fans + 140mm Rear Fan - Black
fields.description: Inspired by sports cars, the Level 20 RS ARGB has a rising top panel that cleverly hides the I/O ports on its side; The ARGB light bar shown on its front perfectly mimics the afterimage of a car’s tail light. It features two tempered glass panels, ATX motherboard support, patented PCI-E slot design and a removable power cover. The Level 20 RS ARGB comes with two preinstalled 200mm 5V ARGB front fans and one 120mm standard rear fan. The front fans are addressable to deliver 16.8 million-color RGB illumination and unparalleled ventilation. By choosing Thermaltake Level 20 RS ARGB, users can experience the best liquid cooling expansion and advanced cable management. Get ready for your race by choosing the new Level 20 RS ARGB. The Level 20 RS ARGB takes our latest case innovations and wraps them in an ultra-modern and sports style that’s utterly unique in the case market today. Stand out from the crowd with the Level 20 RS.

fields.name: Azza CSAZ-804V Pyramid Innovative PC Case W/RGB Fan, Black
fields.description: The innovative Pyramid 804 receives an update! Why have an average case, when your case can be extraordinary? Enter the AZZA Pyramid 804V, with its unique pyramid shape design and pleasing aesthetic. The case features four tempered glass side panels on all four faces, allowing you to show off your beautiful build from all angles. A 120mm Hurricane II digital RGB fan is included, letting you customize its color to your heart’s content. The Pyramid 804V is not just for show: it is able to support most builds that would fit inside any conventional mid-tower case, such as an EATX motherboard, 300mm long video card, 2x2.5” drive bays, 1x3.5” drive bay, and water cooling radiators up to 360mm on the bottom of the case. As this is an updated version of the original 804 model, the 804V allows the video card to be inserted directly into the motherboard without the need for an extension cable, resulting in it being mounted the way it's supposed to. No matter which way you go with this case, it will prove to be a functional and eye-pleasing case in any circumstance.

fields.name: CORSAIR - DOMINATOR PLATINUM RGB 32GB (2Pk 16GB) 5.2GHz DDR5 DIMM Desktop Memory Kit - Black
fields.description: Push the limits of performance with CORSAIR DOMINATOR PLATINUM RGB DDR5 Memory optimized for Intel®. DDR5 delivers higher frequencies and greater capacities than previous generation memory, helping your system power through complex tasks faster than ever before. With world-renowned design lit by 12 ultra-bright CAPELLIX RGB LEDs, DOMINATOR PLATINUM RGB DDR5 complements the styling and power of the most high-end systems. Hand-sorted, tightly screened memory chips and a custom PCB cooled by patented DHX cooling technology ensure consistently high performance. CORSAIR iCUE software enables RGB lighting customization and synchronization, real-time performance information, and onboard voltage regulation for easier, more controlled overclocking. Supporting Intel XMP 3.0 and backed by a limited lifetime warranty, DOMINATOR PLATINUM RGB DDR5 is in a class of its own.

fields.name: CORSAIR - VENGEANCE 32GB (2Pk 16GB) 5.2GHz DDR5 DIMM Desktop Memory Kit - Black
fields.description: CORSAIR VENGEANCE DDR5, optimized for Intel® motherboards, delivers the higher frequencies and greater capacities of DDR5 technology in a high-quality, compact module that suits your system. Tightly-screened high-frequency memory chips power your PC through faster processing, rendering, and buffering than ever, with onboard voltage regulation for easy, finely controlled overclocking. CORSAIR iCUE software enables real-time frequency monitoring, onboard voltage regulation, and Intel XMP 3.0 profile customization. A distinctive solid aluminum heatspreader keeps your memory cool, while ensuring wide compatibility with a huge range of motherboards and CPU coolers. With a limited lifetime warranty as your guarantee of reliability for years to come, VENGEANCE DDR5 continues a long-standing legacy of memory performance.

fields.name: ADATA - XPG SPECTRIX D50 16GB 2x8GB 3.2GHz CL16 RGB Desktop Memory - Gray
fields.description: Reaching speeds of up to 4800MHz and sporting a maximum capacity of 32GB, the XPG SPECTRIX D50 is a monster of a memory module. It also has looks to kill with an elegant styling with geometric lines. Made with only the highest quality chips and PCBs, the D50 provides ultimate stability, reliability, and speeds of up to 4800MHz. What’s more, it supports the latest Intel X299 and AMD TR40 platforms. The D50 sports a solidly constructed 1.95mm-thick metal heatsink for excellent durability. The D50 features a clean and elegant exterior with simple geometric lines and a triangular RGB panel that fits in perfectly with the modules overall design. With the XPG RGB Sync app or a RGB software from a major motherboard brand, switch between three RGB modes - Static, Breathing, and Comet. In addition to the three modes, you can also set it to Music mode to sync with your favorite jams. The D50 supports Intel XMP 2.0 for hassle-free and stable overclocking without the need to go into BIOS.

fields.name: GIGABYTE - Z690 AORUS MASTER Socket 1700 USB 3.2 Intel Motherboard with RGB Lighting - Black
fields.description: The King of Gaming is here. The Z690 AORUS MASTER supports 12th Gen Intel Processors and unparalled performance. GIGABYTE Z690 motherboards come with upgraded power design, high grade storage standards, and outstanding connectivity that enables you to optimize your performance.

fields.name: NZXT - Z590 (Socket LGA 1200) USB 3.2 Intel Motherboard with Wifi
fields.description: Designed around Intel’s Z590 chipset, the N7 Z590 lays the groundwork for a stunning gaming PC build. Features include built-in Wi-Fi 6E connectivity, integrated fan controller, RGB accessories supported across all manufacturers, and more. The motherboard cover perfectly matches the color and finish of your NZXT case, creating a visually seamless backdrop for your components.
